cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP prevents F1 interface connection establishment, leading to DU unavailability.

du.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
du.explanation_en: Altering the remote N address to an incorrect IP causes F1 network interface routing failures, disrupting CU-DU communication.
